msgid ""
"Install Klein for Ray from source, select optional integrations, and keep"
" every Ray worker on a compatible environment."
msgstr "从源码安装 Klein for Ray、选择可选集成，并确保每个 Ray worker 使用兼容的运行环境。"

msgid "Install Klein for Ray"
msgstr "安装 Klein for Ray"

msgid ""
"Klein is currently alpha software. This guide installs it from a source "
"checkout or from an artifact that you build from that checkout; it does "
"not assume that a `ray-klein` distribution is available from PyPI."
msgstr "Klein 目前是 Alpha 软件。本指南介绍如何从源码 checkout 或由该 checkout 构建的制品进行安装；不假定 PyPI 上已有可用的 `ray-klein` 发行包。"

msgid "Supported environment"
msgstr "支持的环境"

msgid "Component"
msgstr "组件"

msgid "Supported range"
msgstr "支持范围"

msgid "Notes"
msgstr "说明"

msgid "Python"
msgstr "Python"

msgid "3.10, 3.11, or 3.12"
msgstr "3.10、3.11 或 3.12"

msgid "Use the same minor version on the driver and workers."
msgstr "driver 和 worker 应使用相同的次版本。"

msgid "Ray"
msgstr "Ray"

msgid "`ray[data]>=2.56.1,<2.57`"
msgstr "`ray[data]>=2.56.1,<2.57`"

msgid ""
"Klein pins one Ray minor because some Ray Data extension points are "
"Developer APIs."
msgstr "Klein 固定使用一个 Ray 次版本，因为部分 Ray Data 扩展点属于 Developer API。"

msgid "Operating system"
msgstr "操作系统"

msgid "Linux or macOS"
msgstr "Linux 或 macOS"

msgid ""
"These are the platforms declared by the package metadata. Other platforms"
" are not part of the current support target."
msgstr "这些是包元数据声明的平台。其他平台不属于当前支持目标。"

msgid "Project maturity"
msgstr "项目成熟度"

msgid "Alpha"
msgstr "Alpha"

msgid "Public APIs and checkpoint formats can still change before 1.0."
msgstr "公共 API 和 checkpoint 格式在 1.0 之前仍可能发生变化。"

msgid ""
"The base installation also constrains NumPy to `<3`, pandas to `<3`, "
"protobuf to `<7`, and SQLGlot to `>=30.12,<31`. Let the package resolver "
"install these dependencies instead of overriding them independently. Read"
" [Compatibility](compatibility.md) before changing Python, Ray, protobuf,"
" or checkpoint-producing Klein versions."
msgstr "基础安装还将 NumPy 限制为 `<3`、pandas 限制为 `<3`、protobuf 限制为 `<7`，并将 SQLGlot 限制为 `>=30.12,<31`。请让包解析器安装这些依赖，不要单独覆盖其版本。在更改 Python、Ray、protobuf 或生成 checkpoint 的 Klein 版本前，请阅读[兼容性](compatibility.md)。"

msgid ""
"Use an isolated environment so another Ray application cannot silently "
"widen the supported Ray range:"
msgstr "请使用隔离环境，避免其他 Ray 应用悄然放宽受支持的 Ray 版本范围："

msgid "Regular installation from a checkout"
msgstr "从 checkout 常规安装"

msgid ""
"Clone the repository, then perform a non-editable installation for "
"ordinary use:"
msgstr "克隆仓库，然后为常规使用执行非 editable 安装："

msgid ""
"This builds and installs the current checkout plus the base dependencies,"
" including `ray[data]`. The installed code does not change when the "
"checkout is edited; reinstall it to pick up a new revision."
msgstr "这会构建并安装当前 checkout 及包括 `ray[data]` 在内的基础依赖。编辑 checkout 不会改变已安装的代码；如需使用新修订，请重新安装。"

msgid ""
"If your organization builds a wheel from a reviewed checkout, install "
"that same wheel on the driver and workers:"
msgstr "如果组织从已审核的 checkout 构建 wheel，请在 driver 和 worker 上安装同一个 wheel："

msgid ""
"Klein contributes the `ray.klein` namespace. It does not replace Ray's "
"`ray/__init__.py`; both the compatible Ray package and Klein must be "
"installed in the same environment."
msgstr "Klein 提供 `ray.klein` 命名空间，但不会替换 Ray 的 `ray/__init__.py`；兼容的 Ray 包和 Klein 必须安装在同一环境中。"

msgid "Editable source installation"
msgstr "Editable 源码安装"

msgid "Use an editable installation when experimenting with the source tree:"
msgstr "试验源码树时，请使用 editable 安装："

msgid ""
"Python code changes are then visible without reinstalling. Re-run the "
"install after changing `pyproject.toml`, switching to a revision with "
"different dependencies, or selecting another optional extra."
msgstr "此后无需重新安装即可看到 Python 代码变更。修改 `pyproject.toml`、切换到依赖不同的修订或选择其他可选 extra 后，请重新执行安装。"

msgid "Contributor installation"
msgstr "贡献者安装"

msgid ""
"The `dev` extra includes every integration, the documentation and test "
"dependencies, pre-commit, and Ruff:"
msgstr "`dev` extra 包含所有集成、文档与测试依赖、pre-commit 和 Ruff："

msgid "Run the normal contributor checks with:"
msgstr "使用以下命令运行常规贡献者检查："

msgid ""
"Integration tests start a managed local Ray cluster, while external-"
"service tests are opt-in. See [Testing](testing.md) for the test tiers "
"and commands."
msgstr "集成测试会启动一个受管理的本地 Ray 集群，外部服务测试则需主动启用。测试分层和命令请参阅[测试](testing.md)。"

msgid "Optional extras"
msgstr "可选 extras"

msgid ""
"Install only the integrations used by the application. Extras can be "
"combined, for example `python -m pip install -e \".[kafka,rocksdb]\"` in "
"an editable checkout."
msgstr "只安装应用使用的集成。Extras 可以组合使用，例如在 editable checkout 中运行 `python -m pip install -e \".[kafka,rocksdb]\"`。"

msgid "Extra"
msgstr "Extra"

msgid "Installed dependencies"
msgstr "安装的依赖"

msgid "Use it for"
msgstr "用途"

msgid "`kafka`"
msgstr "`kafka`"

msgid "`confluent-kafka>=2.3,<3`"
msgstr "`confluent-kafka>=2.3,<3`"

msgid "Bounded or continuous Kafka input and Kafka output."
msgstr "有界或连续 Kafka 输入，以及 Kafka 输出。"

msgid "`iceberg`"
msgstr "`iceberg`"

msgid "`pyiceberg>=0.11.1,<0.12`"
msgstr "`pyiceberg>=0.11.1,<0.12`"

msgid ""
"Iceberg catalog access and batch or checkpointed append output. Catalog-"
"specific dependencies may still be required."
msgstr "Iceberg catalog 访问，以及批处理或基于 checkpoint 的追加输出。可能仍需安装特定 catalog 的依赖。"

msgid "`rocketmq`"
msgstr "`rocketmq`"

msgid "`rocketmq-client-python>=2,<3`"
msgstr "`rocketmq-client-python>=2,<3`"

msgid ""
"Continuous RocketMQ input. A compatible native `librocketmq` is also "
"required on every executing worker."
msgstr "连续 RocketMQ 输入。每个执行任务的 worker 还需要兼容的原生 `librocketmq`。"

msgid "`redis`"
msgstr "`redis`"

msgid "`redis>=5,<7`"
msgstr "`redis>=5,<7`"

msgid "Redis lookup, filtering, and output."
msgstr "Redis 查找、过滤和输出。"

msgid "`rocksdb`"
msgstr "`rocksdb`"

msgid "`rocksdict>=0.3.29,<0.4`"
msgstr "`rocksdict>=0.3.29,<0.4`"

msgid "The node-local RocksDB managed-state backend."
msgstr "节点本地的 RocksDB 托管状态后端。"

msgid "`serve`"
msgstr "`serve`"

msgid "`aiohttp>=3.13.3`, `orjson>=3.9`, and compatible `ray[serve]`"
msgstr "`aiohttp>=3.13.3`、`orjson>=3.9` 和兼容的 `ray[serve]`"

msgid "Ray Serve execution regions and the embedded proxy client."
msgstr "Ray Serve 执行区域和嵌入式代理客户端。"

msgid "`all`"
msgstr "`all`"

msgid "All runtime integrations above"
msgstr "上述所有运行时集成"

msgid ""
"An integration-development environment; it does not include test or "
"documentation tools."
msgstr "集成开发环境；不包含测试或文档工具。"

msgid "`test`"
msgstr "`test`"

msgid "pytest, build/audit tools, testcontainers, and test-only Iceberg support"
msgstr "pytest、构建/审计工具、testcontainers，以及仅供测试使用的 Iceberg 支持"

msgid "Running the repository test suites."
msgstr "运行仓库测试套件。"

msgid "`docs`"
msgstr "`docs`"

msgid "Sphinx, MyST, the PyData theme, copybutton, and sphinx-design"
msgstr "Sphinx、MyST、PyData 主题、copybutton 和 sphinx-design"

msgid "Building this documentation."
msgstr "构建本文档。"

msgid "`dev`"
msgstr "`dev`"

msgid "`all`, `docs`, `test`, pre-commit, and Ruff"
msgstr "`all`、`docs`、`test`、pre-commit 和 Ruff"

msgid "Full contributor setup."
msgstr "完整的贡献者环境。"

msgid ""
"The [connector catalog](connectors/index.md) gives each connector's "
"execution modes, data shape, configuration, and delivery guarantee. A "
"connector may also need a broker, database driver, filesystem credential "
"provider, or native library that cannot be supplied by a Python extra."
msgstr "[连接器目录](connectors/index.md)列出了每个连接器的执行模式、数据形态、配置和交付保证。连接器还可能需要 Python extra 无法提供的 broker、数据库驱动、文件系统凭据提供程序或原生库。"

msgid "Keep the cluster environment consistent"
msgstr "保持集群环境一致"

msgid ""
"Installing Klein only on the submission machine is insufficient. Every "
"Ray worker that can run a Klein source, operator, sink, or user function "
"needs:"
msgstr "只在提交机器上安装 Klein 并不足够。每个可能运行 Klein source、operator、sink 或用户函数的 Ray worker 都需要："

msgid "the same Klein artifact and compatible Ray version;"
msgstr "相同的 Klein 制品和兼容的 Ray 版本；"

msgid "the extras imported by that graph;"
msgstr "该计算图导入的 extras；"

msgid "application modules and user-function dependencies;"
msgstr "应用模块和用户函数依赖；"

msgid "native libraries such as `librocketmq`; and"
msgstr "`librocketmq` 等原生库；以及"

msgid "compatible credentials and filesystem drivers for external services."
msgstr "外部服务所需的兼容凭据和文件系统驱动。"

msgid ""
"Prefer one immutable container image or one versioned wheel set across "
"the Ray head and workers. A Ray runtime environment is also suitable when"
" it installs the same immutable artifacts on every eligible node. Do not "
"install packages from inside a user function: different worker startup "
"times and dependency resolution can make deployment nondeterministic."
msgstr "Ray head 和 worker 应优先使用同一个不可变容器镜像或同一套带版本的 wheel。如果 Ray runtime environment 会在每个符合条件的节点上安装相同的不可变制品，也可以使用它。不要在用户函数内部安装包：不同的 worker 启动时间和依赖解析可能使部署变得不确定。"

msgid ""
"If imports succeed on the driver but fail remotely, compare the "
"interpreter, `ray-klein`, Ray, and extra versions inside the failing "
"worker image. See [Deploy Klein jobs](deployment.md) for Ray Jobs, "
"containers, and KubeRay guidance."
msgstr "如果在 driver 上导入成功、远程却失败，请比较故障 worker 镜像中的解释器、`ray-klein`、Ray 和 extra 版本。有关 Ray Jobs、容器和 KubeRay 的说明，请参阅[部署 Klein 作业](deployment.md)。"

msgid "Verify the installation"
msgstr "验证安装"

msgid "Check the selected interpreter and installed distribution metadata:"
msgstr "检查所选解释器和已安装发行包的元数据："

msgid "From a source checkout, run the bounded smoke test as well:"
msgstr "从源码 checkout 安装时，还请运行有界 smoke test："

msgid ""
"The import and version checks do not start a Ray cluster. The example "
"starts or reuses the runtime needed by its bounded Ray Data execution."
msgstr "导入和版本检查不会启动 Ray 集群。该示例会启动或复用其有界 Ray Data 执行所需的运行时。"

msgid "Upgrade or change extras"
msgstr "升级或更改 extras"

msgid ""
"Review [Upgrade Klein jobs](upgrading.md) and "
"[Compatibility](compatibility.md) before upgrading an application that "
"must restore checkpoints. Then update the checkout and reinstall the "
"required extras:"
msgstr "升级必须恢复 checkpoint 的应用前，请先查看[升级 Klein 作业](upgrading.md)和[兼容性](compatibility.md)。然后更新 checkout 并重新安装所需 extras："

msgid "For an editable contributor environment, re-run:"
msgstr "对于 editable 贡献者环境，请重新运行："

msgid ""
"Do not upgrade Ray past the declared `<2.57` bound independently. For a "
"production cluster, build a new immutable environment, rehearse "
"checkpoint restore against production-shaped state, and follow the "
"cutover procedure in [Deploy Klein jobs](deployment.md#upgrade-"
"procedure)."
msgstr "不要单独将 Ray 升级到声明的 `<2.57` 上界之外。对于生产集群，请构建新的不可变环境，使用与生产形态相同的状态演练 checkpoint 恢复，并遵循[部署 Klein 作业](deployment.md#upgrade-procedure)中的切换流程。"

msgid "Uninstall"
msgstr "卸载"

msgid "Remove Klein with the interpreter that owns the installation:"
msgstr "使用拥有该安装的解释器移除 Klein："

msgid ""
"Pip does not automatically remove dependencies that were installed "
"through Klein's extras. Review them before uninstalling anything shared "
"with another application. An editable uninstall removes the environment "
"link but does not delete the source checkout. Do not manually delete the "
"surrounding `ray` package: Ray is a separate distribution."
msgstr "Pip 不会自动移除通过 Klein extras 安装的依赖。卸载与其他应用共享的任何内容前，请先核查这些依赖。卸载 editable 安装只会移除环境链接，不会删除源码 checkout。不要手动删除外围的 `ray` 包：Ray 是独立的发行包。"

msgid "Troubleshoot installation"
msgstr "排查安装问题"

msgid "Symptom"
msgstr "现象"

msgid "Check and fix"
msgstr "检查与修复"

msgid "Pip rejects the Python version"
msgstr "Pip 拒绝当前 Python 版本"

msgid ""
"Run `python --version`. Create a Python 3.10–3.12 environment and invoke "
"pip as `python -m pip`."
msgstr "运行 `python --version`。创建 Python 3.10–3.12 环境，并以 `python -m pip` 调用 pip。"

msgid "The resolver reports a Ray conflict"
msgstr "解析器报告 Ray 冲突"

msgid ""
"Another package requires a Ray version outside `>=2.56.1,<2.57`. Use a "
"separate environment rather than widening Klein's bound without "
"compatibility testing."
msgstr "另一个包要求使用 `>=2.56.1,<2.57` 之外的 Ray 版本。请使用独立环境，不要在未经兼容性测试的情况下放宽 Klein 的版本约束。"

msgid "`ModuleNotFoundError: ray.klein`"
msgstr "`ModuleNotFoundError: ray.klein`"

msgid ""
"Confirm `python -m pip show ray-klein` uses the same interpreter as the "
"application. Merely placing the checkout beside an installed Ray package "
"is not an installation."
msgstr "确认 `python -m pip show ray-klein` 与应用使用同一个解释器。仅将 checkout 放在已安装的 Ray 包旁边并不等于完成安装。"

msgid "`ray-klein: command not found`"
msgstr "`ray-klein: command not found`"

msgid ""
"Activate the environment and confirm its `bin` directory is on `PATH`. "
"Reinstall the project to create the console entry point."
msgstr "激活环境并确认其 `bin` 目录位于 `PATH` 中。重新安装项目以创建控制台入口点。"

msgid "A connector module is missing"
msgstr "缺少连接器模块"

msgid ""
"Install its named extra on the driver and every eligible worker, then "
"restart or redeploy those processes."
msgstr "在 driver 和每个符合条件的 worker 上安装对应名称的 extra，然后重启或重新部署这些进程。"

msgid "RocketMQ loads in Python but cannot load its client library"
msgstr "Python 能加载 RocketMQ，但无法加载其客户端库"

msgid ""
"Install a compatible native `librocketmq` in the worker image and make it"
" available to the platform dynamic linker."
msgstr "在 worker 镜像中安装兼容的原生 `librocketmq`，并确保平台动态链接器可以找到它。"

msgid "The driver imports a dependency but a Ray task cannot"
msgstr "driver 能导入依赖，但 Ray task 无法导入"

msgid ""
"The cluster environments differ. Deploy the same wheel/image and extras "
"to all nodes; a local driver virtual environment is not propagated "
"automatically."
msgstr "集群环境不一致。请将相同的 wheel/镜像和 extras 部署到所有节点；本地 driver 虚拟环境不会自动传播。"

msgid "`python -m pip check` reports protobuf or SQLGlot conflicts"
msgstr "`python -m pip check` 报告 protobuf 或 SQLGlot 冲突"

msgid ""
"Keep the bounds declared by `pyproject.toml`, or isolate Klein from the "
"application requiring the incompatible version."
msgstr "请遵守 `pyproject.toml` 声明的版本范围，或将 Klein 与需要不兼容版本的应用隔离。"

msgid "Installation succeeds but the CLI cannot connect"
msgstr "安装成功，但 CLI 无法连接"

msgid ""
"This is a cluster connection issue, not an import issue. Start or select "
"a Ray cluster and see [CLI reference](cli-reference.md#connect-to-the-"
"ray-cluster) and [Troubleshooting](troubleshooting.md)."
msgstr "这是集群连接问题，而不是导入问题。请启动或选择 Ray 集群，并参阅 [CLI 参考](cli-reference.md#connect-to-the-ray-cluster)和[故障排查](troubleshooting.md)。"
